<section class="section quality-assurance">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-image">
        <div class="image-placeholder">
          <span><svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></span>
          <p>Quality Guaranteed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-text">
        <span class="section-label">WHY BUY FROM US</span>
        <h2>Why Choose a Trusted Cannabis Dispensary Near Me?</h2>
        <p>
          Looking for a cannabis dispensary near me that you can actually trust? When you buy weed online from us, you get products that meet real quality standards. Every product is independently lab-tested — no mystery content, no contaminated garbage.
        </p>
        <p>
          We provide complete transparency: exact THC/CBD percentages, terpene profiles, and confirmation that there are no pesticides, heavy metals, or contamination. This is what buying weed should look like — not some mystery bag from a mate's mate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits-section">
      <span class="section-label">OUR STANDARDS</span>
      <h3>What Sets Us Apart</h3>
      <div class="content-two-col">
        <div>
          <h4><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:6px;"><path d="M6 18h8"/><path d="M3 22h18"/><path d="M14 22a7 7 0 1 0 0-14h-1"/><path d="M9 14h2"/><path d="M9 2v6"/><path d="M13 2v6"/><path d="M9 8h4"/></svg>Laboratory Tested</h4>
          <p>
            Every batch of product is sent to independent Australian laboratories for comprehensive testing. We test for cannabinoid potency (THC, CBD, and minor cannabinoids), pesticide residues, heavy metals, and microbial contamination. Only products that pass our rigorous standards make it to our shelves.
          </p>
          <h4><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:6px;"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1"/></svg>Full Compliance</h4>
          <p>
            We operate in full compliance with Australian therapeutic goods regulations. Our products are sourced from approved cultivators and manufacturers who meet TGA requirements for medicinal cannabis production.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:6px;"><path d="M12.586 2.586A2 2 0 0 0 11.172 2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7.172a2 2 0 0 0 .586 1.414l8.704 8.704a2.426 2.426 0 0 0 3.42 0l6.58-6.58a2.426 2.426 0 0 0 0-3.42z"/><circle cx="7.5" cy="7.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"/></svg>Proper Labelling</h4>
          <p>
            All our products come with accurate, detailed labelling including cannabinoid content, dosage recommendations, ingredients, batch numbers, and expiry dates. You always know exactly what you're getting.
          </p>
          <h4><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:-3px;margin-right:6px;"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>Patient Support</h4>
          <p>
            Our team includes qualified cannabis consultants who can help guide you to the right products for your needs. We're here to answer questions about strains, dosages, and consumption methods to ensure you get the best therapeutic outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quality-assurance {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .content-text h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .content-text p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefits-section {
    padding-top: 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .benefits-section h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .benefits-section h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 25px 0 15px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content-two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .content-two-col p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 60px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
    min-height: 500px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder span {
    font-size: 6rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .image-placeholder p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .content-two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      min-height: 300px;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .image-placeholder span {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
